app_description: Diary Book is a lovely diary app that can record mood and keep a diary. Accumulate your feelings day by day record your daily life and keep good memories in Mood Diary. Our Features Mood Calendar: super cute little expression to record your daily mood Hand Book Cover: create your own lovely hand book and collect your own life s hand book. Graphic Stickers: rich and lovely stickers graphic collage materials make your hand account more fresh and beautiful anytime and anywhere. Calendar: convenient for querying calendar dates. Graphic Diary: write a diary for the next day and add pictures. Dynamic theme: multiple home page dynamic theme styles to decorate your page. Our Expectations Writing morning records every morning summarizing and reflecting every night can bring a sense of ritual to our daily life. When we open the hand account records in emotions this whole record is our own history . I hope you can look back on the past and record everything beautiful through Emotion. If you like Emotion and have any questions or comments in use please leave your feedback.
